|CKBStretch Poison: One Dose, More Regret|000

Syntax: stretchpoison <poison> onto <weapon>

At Rank 3, Contraband 2, and Alchemy 100, consume a prepared poison and cut it
into a weaker dose that clings to a compatible weapon for longer. Better
Alchemy improves the result.

You must bring the poison; Charlatans improve delivery rather than replacing
the poison trade. The weapon must be carried, unwielded, ordinary, and able to
take a poison treatment. The installer is always poisoned during the work.
This proves the mixture is genuine and saves money on laboratory animals.
